{
  "id": "RAW_f1683049",
  "title": "Claude Code 之父的 13 大 cc 使用技巧",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2OTA1OTAxNA==&mid=2247487765&idx=1&sn=a3c229346e7b7d66e179058ae0a34e87",
  "date": "2026-01-03 02:35:00",
  "author": "花叔",
  "siteName": "花叔",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #faf9f7 !important;padding: 20px 24px 56px 24px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">一大早起来在X上看到Boris Cherny发了条长帖，分享他自己怎么用Claude Code的。感觉是我2026年看到最有价值的一条内容了。所以很想在这里也给大家完整分享下。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004099\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db5bcffa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSibLLZPS6Tj2jW0VqtC3HS0k6nofOUpHy3QaRqPkMsgjIcc0Zzc6LQqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris是Claude Code的创建者。2024年9月，他把Claude Code作为副项目做出来，没想到后来成了AI编程领域最火的工具之一。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">创建者亲自出来写使用技巧，这很难得。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他是真的懂这个产品的优势和缺陷的，从他的视角肯定能获得一些不一样的启发。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">更让我有信心的是，他是真的在长期高频使用自己的产品。前段时间他发过一条推文：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004101\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1defe3a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSnOBTPmiclSj1Q1wibbcG5njSEFvqMnMaHsIzG2oUYibUpU4LJD2qOBwBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding: 16px 24px;border-left: 4px solid #C15F3C;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.55 !important;font-style: italic;border-radius: 8px;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去30天，我提交了259个PR——497次commit，新增4万行代码，删除3.8万行。每一行都是Claude Code + Opus 4.5写的。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他还晒了自己的使用数据：47天里有46天都在用，最长连续使用42天，最长单次session跑了1天18小时50分钟，总共消耗了3.25亿tokens。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004097\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ebccd4b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSiaA3bQyN5CenmGUwDLPPicwE1kDckeAbAox4xjCyYyPmHP9fsGDm4wQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">看到创建者本人是这么用自己产品的，确实让人对cc更有信心。毕竟很多产品的创始人自己都不怎么用自己做的东西。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">回到这次的13条技巧。Boris在推文开头说：</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding: 16px 24px;border-left: 4px solid #C15F3C;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.55 !important;font-style: italic;border-radius: 8px;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的配置可能出乎意料地朴素！Claude Code开箱即用就很好，所以我个人并没有太多自定义。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">仔细看完13条建议，确实不是什么神秘hack，但出奇的实用，给我带来不少启发，希望对你也是！</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 并行跑5个Claude</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris在终端里同时运行5个Claude Code实例，标签页编号1-5，用系统通知来知道哪个需要输入。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004100\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cbb463e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSpftaH01fggc0C48ic2sQrFo7Tic42BWgWYFeLibCJfREaAjBymU2ZJhnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这点我之前也提过，不过我更习惯在Cursor、Trae等IDE里开5-10个终端跑不同任务，相互没有干扰。因为我不只是用Claude Code写代码，还会让他写脚本、写文章之类的，所以用IDE看看cc跑的成果我觉得会更方便。但总之一次性开多个cc窗口，去多完成一些任务的思维我是完全认可的，Boris这个系统通知的思路也确实优雅。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 本地+网页双线作战</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了本地5个Claude，Boris还在claude.ai/code上同时跑5-10个。&nbsp;用</span><code><span leaf=\"\">&amp;</span></code><span leaf=\"\">把本地会话交接到网页端，或者用</span><code><span leaf=\"\">--teleport</span></code><span leaf=\"\">在两边切换。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004098\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71f2d679&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSfbVdkTKZIfP6FzBMm031eicK5KSZ2wG6l77v2XS3OsFic8sCGPQDFcmg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个我之前完全没用过。我一直只在终端用，没意识到他们网页端居然做得这么好了。我打算试试了，毕竟平时外出拿手机就能用网页去控制cc的产出，也真是一刻不耽误。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://claude.ai/code\" target=\"_blank\">https://claude.ai/code</a></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 全程用Opus 4.5 + 思考模式</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris说所有工作都用Opus 4.5，并开启思考模式。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他的理由是：虽然Opus比Sonnet更大更慢，但因为你需要更少的引导，工具使用能力更强，最终几乎总是比用小模型更快。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这点我完全认同，除了慢一点，以及费钱外，Opus 4.5真的没啥缺点。当然，「贵」这事也不算Claude的问题，是我的问题，我最近又把Claude Max给续订回来了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004102\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0c9721d3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSbowR4yibZibejEgAe9NH88JMfX18yK1yJVzEtdqeiatglWJbozIkAVdMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.&nbsp;团队共享CLAUDE.md</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris团队共享同一个CLAUDE.md文件，check进git，整个团队每周都会贡献多次。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键机制：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">每当看到Claude做错了什么，就加到CLAUDE.md里，这样Claude下次就知道不要这么做了。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这形成了一个飞轮：Claude犯错 → 记录 → Claude学会 → 犯更少的错。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004103\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d596366d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mS1IiaV4nZib714nExoD5GSh649PFCkZNX7G5o5cLibmnSrMZwSCGbPD8tg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个思路我完全认可。CLAUDE.md并不是一次性的文档，你应该里面不停更新，让cc的运行规则更符合你的要求。比如我的写作Agent的CLAUDE.md文档已经迭代了几十次...大版本号都更新到6.0了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004106\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2554c4f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSn6HqdzvsoKzOZJo3VVReXzYia9gwgnicZMoCjia5SeK6SqU0r0PovfFtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">5. Code Review时自动更新规则</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris在代码审查时，会在同事的PR上@.claude，让它把某条规则加到CLAUDE.md中。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们用Claude Code的GitHub Action来实现。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">设置：</span><code><span leaf=\"\">/install-github-action</span></code></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004105\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6cdf6cc6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSabdZM4FFVyob3gIRdUg9Qpt6SYYktrOedjCh1zlwefsdib2lMaGTeLg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">6. 大多数会话从Plan模式开始</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris说大多数会话都从Plan模式开始（按两次shift+tab）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">流程是：先用Plan模式来回讨论直到满意计划，然后切换到自动接受编辑模式，Claude通常能一次完成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他强调：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个好的计划真的很重要！</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004104\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eca6bfcc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSrOia217EeMaV7hIPPUvFPfpUpLxkE9Auue9TZXqxM0TvbkcEZ79LWPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这点确实。直接让Claude开干，经常做到一半发现方向错了。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">7. 斜杠命令用于高频工作流</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris对每天重复做很多次的\"内循环\"工作流都用斜杠命令，放在</span><code><span leaf=\"\">.claude/commands/</span></code><span leaf=\"\">目录下。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键是：这不只是节省打字，还能让Claude自己也调用这些命令。比如Claude写代码时可以调用你定义的</span><code><span leaf=\"\">/review</span></code><span leaf=\"\">来自己检查。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004107\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35bc0d2b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSsFeU60zPiaYNUtRU7NdYHJGtpelUVqEWzGibZrffz7ibdoxUGQRycPoqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">8. 用子代理自动化常见流程</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris用几个子代理：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">code-simplifier：Claude工作完成后简化代码</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">verify-app：端到端测试的详细指令</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他把子代理看作自动化大多数PR都要做的工作流。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004108\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f28fb038&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSF9Okkn4ibYt5H7VzNcl41vuY5RYAveYBELCfuFwgezwRMicfoaFicSPkw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这里有个坑：不要搞一堆\"专家子代理\"（Python专家、前端专家），这会把上下文分割开，让主Claude无法整体推理。用子代理做\"流程自动化\"是对的，但不要用来做\"专家分工\"。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">9. PostToolUse钩子自动格式化</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们用PostToolUse钩子来格式化Claude的代码。Claude通常开箱就能生成格式良好的代码，钩子处理最后10%，避免后续CI中的格式错误。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004109\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=da1bff58&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mS2JlC1iakF1YaS4XUltQa36XjwM3VB70BNzAydQUsLwFbOQibriaGEeSqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个思路可以推广：用钩子在关键检查点做验证，而不是限制每一步动作。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">10. 用/permissions预授权，而非跳过权限</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris说他不使用</span><code><span leaf=\"\">--dangerously-skip-permissions</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他用</span><code><span leaf=\"\">/permissions</span></code><span leaf=\"\">预先允许已知安全的bash命令，大部分设置check进</span><code><span leaf=\"\">.claude/settings.json</span></code><span leaf=\"\">并与团队共享。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004111\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=72b93c42&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mS7yovjaEnia3GqNJLSp7dFYqYWokXaplUKzSzia1JoOlFibtuG6FGvX2Tg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈哈，这点来说，我倒是更激进一些，我每次默认启动cc的时候都是允许所有命令自动运行的，至今没出过事。但是这个就看个人性格吧，看喜欢安全地慢慢确认，还是接受一些风险，但是要更自动化。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">11. Claude使用所有工具</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris让Claude Code帮他用各种工具：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">通过MCP服务器搜索和发Slack消息</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">运行BigQuery查询回答分析问题</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">从Sentry抓取错误日志</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">确实，Claude Code的定位不只是\"写代码的工具\"。我之前用Claude Code + Chrome Devtools MCP做B站和YouTube的自动回复，让Claude Code翻译Paul Graham的100篇文章，都是把它当成通用Agent在用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004110\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=16e598b1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mSMQGLOTa1qGV7jIvZsvYgMokU35BdjxelmaicibGvibSnDkkVlJ6DgUIyg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">12. 长任务的处理策略</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于非常长的任务，Boris用三种方式：</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">提示Claude完成后用后台代理验证</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">用agent Stop钩子做验证</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">使用ralph-wiggum插件（让Claude自动循环直到完成）</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">ralph-wiggum这个名字来自《辛普森一家》的角色，核心是让Claude在完成后自动继续，直到真正达到目标。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">插件：</span><code><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/ralph-wiggum\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/ralph-wiggum</a></span></code></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004112\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b601f454&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mScj83S29eGlniaHF6PADvcB9yok1wIwL1zdt40PeAQpxASGORdheaibIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">13. 最重要的建议：给Claude验证工作的方式</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris说这是从Claude Code获得最佳结果的最重要的事：</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding: 16px 24px;border-left: 4px solid #C15F3C;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.55 !important;font-style: italic;border-radius: 8px;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">给Claude一种验证工作的方式。如果Claude有这个反馈循环，最终结果的质量会提升2-3倍。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他的做法是用Chrome扩展测试每一个改动：Claude打开浏览器，测试UI，迭代直到代码正常工作。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">验证在每个领域不同：可能是运行bash命令，或跑测试套件，或在浏览器/手机模拟器中测试。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">确保在这个环节投入精力。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100004113\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6d2e2bc5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHbwxhdpb04pyVE1VJbZj6mS1v5MYt5c3CnQXnKhu52M3a5IagJDTXEStYmf1wTUILVcPWfBEgsdlg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这点确实是最有价值的洞察。很多时候让Claude写完代码就完事了，没有给它验证的机会。但如果Claude能自己测试、自己发现问题、自己修复，质量会好很多。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;margin: 56px 0 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C15F3C 0%, #9DC88D 100%);-webkit-background-clip: text;background-clip: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">几点感受</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">读完Boris的13条，有几个感受：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">基础功能用到极致比黑魔法更有效。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Boris的配置确实朴素，没什么神秘hack。但他把Plan模式、CLAUDE.md、子代理、钩子这些基础功能用得很彻底。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">并行思维很重要。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;本地5个 + 网页端5-10个，这个并行规模超出我之前想象。我在Cursor里开5个终端跑Claude Code就觉得够多了，Boris直接翻倍。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">验证机制是关键。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;第13条是最重要的：给Claude验证的能力。写代码 → 测试 → 发现问题 → 修复 → 再测试，这个闭环形成了，输出质量就上去了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后，Boris说：</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding: 16px 24px;border-left: 4px solid #C15F3C;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.55 !important;font-style: italic;border-radius: 8px;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code团队的每个人使用方式都非常不同。没有一种\"正确\"的使用方式。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这点我认同。这13条是他的用法，不一定适合每个人。但至少给了一个参考：创建者本人是这么用的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">相关链接</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Boris的原文推文：<a href=\"https://x.com/bcherny/status/2007179832300581177\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/bcherny/status/2007179832300581177</a></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Chrome扩展文档：<a href=\"https://code.claude.com/docs/en/chrome\" target=\"_blank\">https://code.claude.com/docs/en/chrome</a></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ralph Wiggum插件：<a href=\"https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/ralph-wiggum\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/ralph-wiggum</a></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"花叔\" data-alias=\"WatsonBM\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/HRdaeEmxNHaELdMcFibicYol7AFSicksic6clicsmBq99XAP6NdibZI7FyzcgEvtC1MPdQFs9MQxwwYia2MYs1lMibicKdw/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"AI Native Coder：AppStore付费榜第一的「小猫补光灯」app开发者，这个账号主要关注AI、AI编程，也对互联网、商业以及更好的生活保有兴趣。\" data-id=\"Mzg2OTA1OTAxNA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"1\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\">本文首发于我的知识星球「AI编程：从入门到精通」，转载请注明来源：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\"><a href=\"https://t.zsxq.com/BFTPI\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.zsxq.com/BFTPI</a></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Claude Code 创建者 Boris Cherny 分享了 13 个高效使用该 AI 编程工具的技巧，强调并行、团队协作、模型选择及反馈验证机制，以最大化 AI 辅助编程的效率和质量。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Claude Code 创建者 Boris Cherny 分享了 13 个高效使用该 AI 编程工具的技巧，强调并行、团队协作、模型选择及反馈验证机制，以最大化 AI 辅助编程的效率和质量。",
  "summary": "本文详细分享了 Claude Code 创建者 Boris Cherny 使用其 AI 编程工具的 13 个高级技巧。Boris 自己在过去 30 天内提交了 259 个 PR，所有代码均由 Claude Code + Opus 4.5 撰写，证明了其工具的强大效能。这些技巧包括：同时运行多个 Claude Code 实例以提高并行效率、本地与网页端协同工作模式、全程使用 Opus 4.5 确保代码质量、团队共享 CLAUDE.md 文档进行经验积累和错误规避，以及在 Code Review 中自动更新规则。他还强调从 Plan 模式开始规划、使用斜杠命令自动化高频工作流、利用子代理处理常见流程、通过 PostToolUse 钩子自动化代码格式化、谨慎处理权限设置、将 Claude 视为通用 Agent 应用于多场景、以及针对长任务的处理策略。最核心的建议是为 Claude 提供反馈验证机制，通过测试和迭代循环来显著提升代码质量。文章总结，这些技巧虽朴素但实用，强调了基础功能的深度利用、并行思维和有效的验证机制对于最大化 AI 编程效率的重要性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "通过多实例并行和本地/网页协同提升 AI 辅助编程效率。",
      "explanation": "Boris 同时运行 5 个本地 Claude Code 实例和 5-10 个网页端实例，通过系统通知和设备切换实现高效并行处理任务，大幅提升生产力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "利用大型模型（Opus 4.5）和思考模式优化 AI 编程质量。",
      "explanation": "尽管大型模型速度较慢且成本较高，但其更强的理解和工具使用能力减少了人工引导需求，实际工作效率更高，尤其配合思考模式可提升规划和执行力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "构建团队共享的知识库（CLAUDE.md）和自动化规则更新机制。",
      "explanation": "团队通过共享 CLAUDE.md 记录 Claude 的错误并持续更新规则，形成正向反馈循环；结合 GitHub Action 实现代码审查时自动更新规则，提升 AI 学习和适应性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "优先进行详细规划（Plan 模式）和自动化常用工作流（斜杠命令/子代理）。",
      "explanation": "多数会话从 Plan 模式开始，确保 AI 在行动前有清晰且满意的计划；对高频、重复的工作流使用自定义斜杠命令和子代理进行自动化，例如代码简化、自动化测试等。"
    },
    {
      "point": "为 AI 提供明确的反馈和验证机制是提升产出质量的关键。",
      "explanation": "Boris 强调给 Claude 提供验证其工作的能力，如通过 Chrome 扩展测试 UI、运行测试套件、执行 Bash 命令等，形成“编写-测试-修复-迭代”的闭环，显著提升最终代码的质量。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我的配置可能出乎意料地朴素！Claude Code 开箱即用就很好，所以我个人并没有太多自定义。",
    "每当看到 Claude 做错了什么，就加到 CLAUDE.md 里，这样 Claude 下次就知道不要这么做了。",
    "一个好的计划真的很重要！",
    "给 Claude 一种验证工作的方式。如果 Claude 有这个反馈循环，最终结果的质量会提升 2-3 倍。",
    "Claude Code 团队的每个人使用方式都非常不同。没有一种\"正确\"的使用方式。"
  ],
